de.targodan.usb.io.processing

Class DefaultParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.targodan.usb.io.processing.DefaultParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parser

    public class DefaultParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements Parser
    DefaultParser is the default implementation of the Parser interface. It handles parsing of the MechaSqueak commands as well as rat calls and reports and a few extra commands.

      • sanitizeCaseIdentifier

        protected java.lang.String sanitizeCaseIdentifier(java.lang.String caseIdentifier)
        Sanitizes a case identifier. It tries to interpret the identifier first as a case number optionally prefixed by a '#' or a 'c' and returns just the number. If that fails it interprets the identifier as client name and returns the same string as the input.
        Parameters:
        caseIdentifier - The identifier to be sanitized.
        Returns:
        The sanitized case identifier.
